`hu laka fiY Safoqapi", "text_ar": "بَارَكَ ا@للّٰهُ لَكَ فِى صَفْقَةِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yamiynika", "text_ar": "يَمِينِكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May God bless thee in"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the contract"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[(lit."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the striking"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of thy right hand"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SafoqapN raAbiHapN", "text_ar": "صَفْقَةٌ رَابِحَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SafoqapN xaAsirapN", "text_ar": "صَفْقَةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, O, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A sale"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bargain"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bringing gain,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a sale"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bargain occasioning loss"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (K.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~ahu lamubaAraku", "text_ar": "اـِنَّهُ لَمُبَارَكُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlS~afoqapi", "text_ar": "الصَّفْقَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily he is blessed in respect of bargaining"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; meaning that he buys not anything without gaining in it. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qadi A@$otarayotu Alyawoma SafoqapF", "text_ar": "قَدِ ا@شْتَرَيْتُ اليَوْمَ صَفْقَةً"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SaAliHapF", "text_ar": "صَالِحَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I have purchased to-day a good purchase"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlbayoEu SafoqapN A^awo xiyaArN", "text_ar": "البَيْعُ صَفْقَةٌ اَوْ خِيَارٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Selling is decisive or with the option of returning."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh.) And it is said in a trad. (of Ibn-Mes'ood, TA),"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SafoqataAni", "text_ar": "صَفْقَتَانِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fiY SafoqapK ribFA", "text_ar": "فِى صَفْقَةٍ رِبًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Two bargains in a"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[single]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bargain"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "are an unlawful gain"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: this is of two kinds: one is the seller's saying to the buyer, “ I sell to thee such a thing for a hundred dirhems on the condition of thy buying of me this garment, or piece of cloth, for such a sum: ” the other kind is his saying, “ I sell to thee this garment, or piece of cloth, for twenty dirhems on the condition of thy selling to me thy commodity for ten dirhems. ” (O.) And it is said in another trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~a A^akobara AlkabaAy^iri A^ano tuqaAtila A^ahola Safoqatika", "text_ar": "اـِنَّ اَكْبَرَ الكَبَايِرِ اَنْ تُقَاتِلَ اَهْلَ صَفْقَتِكَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily the greatest of great sins is"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thy fighting those with whom thou hast made a covenant:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "because each of the two persons making a covenant puts his hand in the hand of the other, like as is done by each of two persons selling and buying. (TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["Mgh", "K", "M", "TA", "Msb", "S", "O"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}